  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This observational study investigates ICP signals obtained through an external ventricular
      drain in the brain connected with an external transducer. In particular, the study
      investigates how drainage influences the monitored signal: influence of flow rate, reservoir
      height and initial ICP before draining.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
